      "@type": "owl:DatatypeProperty",
      "rdfs:label": "Operator + (Map sum)",
      "rdfs:comment": "Monoidal operator of Gm. Intra-REVOI — closed within Map. Precedence: medium (× > + > |). Example: R + O = ModelQuality.",
